import React, { Component } from 'react' import _ from 'lodash' import { Icon, Menu, Table, Progress } from 'semantic-ui-react' import Pagination from './Pagination' class TableExamplePagination extends Component { render() { const { data, headers } = this.props if (!data) { return null } const { campaigns } = data console.log('this.props', data, headers) return (
{headers && ( {headers.map(header => ( {header.value} ))} )} {campaigns && campaigns.map((part, index) => ( {index + 1} {_.capitalize(part.name)} {_.capitalize(part.campaignType)} {_.capitalize(part.status)} {_.capitalize(part.channel)} Impression : 70 Click : 70 Bounce : 70 Browse: 70 Action ))} 1 {/* 2 3 4 */}
) } } export default TableExamplePagination
